Description: Egypt, beach scene with medium group of male and female adults, standing and sitting on towels. Males wearing shoes, suits, hats. Females wearing dresses, hats. Some holding umbrellas. Male at centre wearing bathing costume. Row of beach huts in background. Medium: Gelatin silver print.
Producer name: Photographed by: John Frederick Clifford Hunt
Curator's comments: Circumstances: The Imperial War Museum holds photographs from the same collection with a more military content - see [HUN-] PIC DOC 66.
